                            펀투를 통해 재밌게 투자해보아요!
                        </p>
                        <a class="btn btn-dark btn-xl" href="#services">서비스 상세</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Services-->
        <section class="content-section bg-primary text-white text-center" id="services">
            <div class="container px-4 px-lg-5">
                <div class="content-section-heading">
                    <h2 class="mb-5">Services</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="row gx-4 gx-lg-5">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                        <span class="service-icon rounded-circle mx-auto mb-3"><i class="icon-screen-smartphone"></i></span>
                        <h4><strong>TALK</strong></h4>
                        <p class="text-faded mb-0">친구들과 함께 소통하며 투자해요</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                        <span class="service-icon rounded-circle mx-auto mb-3"><i class="icon-pencil"></i></span>
                        <h4><strong>LEARN</strong></h4>
                        <p class="text-faded mb-0">성투를 위해 공부해요</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 mb-md-0">
                        <span class="service-icon rounded-circle mx-auto mb-3"><i class="icon-game-controller"></i></span>
                        <h4><strong>PLAY</strong></h4>
                        <p class="text-faded mb-0">재밌게 투자해요</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                        <span class="service-icon rounded-circle mx-auto mb-3"><i class="icon-question"></i></span>
                        <h4><strong>Question</strong></h4>
                        <p class="text-faded mb-0">궁금한건 물어보세요</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Portfolio-->
        <section class="content-section" id="portfolio">
            <div class="container px-4 px-lg-5">
                <div class="content-section-heading text-center">
                    <h2 class="mb-5">최근 게시글</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="row gx-0">
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <a class="portfolio-item" href="https://blog.naver.com/denzelkim/222685742989">
                            <div class="caption">
